    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jules: A Retro Action-Platformer</strong> Step back into the golden era of gaming with <strong>Jules</strong>, a linear action-platformer inspired by the legendary 16-bit classics of the 80s and 90s. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867050/extras/347868682aa18d7e50504232992e6abf.apng?t=1771276345\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867050/extras/347868682aa18d7e50504232992e6abf.poster.avif?t=1771276345\" class=\"bb_img\" width=48 height=48 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The kingdom has fallen. In a heartbeat, the land was overrun by Canc’s relentless army of the undead. Now, it’s up to Jules and his loyal Subweapon Master, <strong>Sir</strong>, to fight their way through the hordes. Your ultimate goal? A final, pulse-pounding showdown within the heart of Canc's castle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Classic Journey:</strong> Traverse through 5 distinct, atmospheric scenarios.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Master the Arsenal:</strong> Use your <strong>whip</strong> and three iconic special weapons—<strong>Sword, Axe, and Cross</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Epic Encounters:</strong> Test your reflexes against 6 boss battles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Authentic Aesthetic:</strong> Pixel art that feels like from your childhood.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Ultimate Challenge:</strong> Ready for more? Tackle the <strong>Hard Mode</strong>, featuring tougher enemies and no special weapons. Only for true masters!<br> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
